name: Soul Ice Cream
description:
This soulmap is extremely complex in smallest details and it is projective, like a giant Rorschach (inkblot) test or a klecksography composition would be, I’ll show myself to you, and no matter for how long or how deep you are studying, you’ll always discover something new, but you’ll always see only yourself in it...

You can play “fantasy soul mapping” games, enlarge the image and look deeper, look from different perspectives, in different moods, put it aside and look again in a few days, ask others what they see, you will be surprised and you’ll see that the image is infinite as such, and is always “changing” with you…

(November 1, 1921 - Dedicating this creation to my Grandfather for his 100th birthday, grateful for all those colourful stories)
